            .card__content
              h3 BitBrawn <span class="card__dates">2021 - Present</span>
              p I founded BitBrawn to rescue aging web applications that have become too fragile to change. If your JavaScript or Rails system is slowing you down, we stabilise it, modernise it, and get it generating value again without a full rebuild.

              p <a href="https://bitbrawn.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Visit BitBrawn</a>

              h4 Recent projects

              ul.technologies
                li <strong><a href="https://dcthomsonshop.co.uk" target="_blank" rel="noopener">DC Thomson</a></strong> &#9758; Rebuilding their subscription purchase platform for better customer experience.
                li <strong><a href="https://laced.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Laced</a></strong> &#9758; Consulting and development support on a major European expansion.
                li <strong><a href="https://riftrefunds.co.uk" target="_blank" rel="noopener">RIFT</a></strong> &#9758; Partnering to digitise and streamline their Tax Refund claims process.
                li <strong><a href="https://purplebricks.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Purplebricks</a></strong> &#9758; Reducing overheads with a self-service property information collection flow.
                li <strong><a href="https://allocate.co.uk" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Allocate</a></strong> &#9758; Leading modernisation and ongoing development of their core web application and API.

        .grid__item
