            .card__aside
              .card__image-container
                img.card__image(src="/assets/images/logos/leaf.svg", alt="Leaf logo" width="80" height="48" loading="lazy")
            .card__content
              h3 Leaf <span class="card__dates">2016 - 2021</span>
              p I co-founded Leaf with a <a href="https://chrisannetts.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">design partner</a>, growing the team to seven designers, developers and project managers and delivering high-impact digital products for UK and US clients. We closed Leaf in 2021 to pursue new projects.

              p <a href="https://weareleaf.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Visit Leaf</a>

              h4 Notable clients

              ul.technologies
                li <strong><a href="https://holidayextras.co.uk" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Holiday Extras</a></strong> &#9758; Played a major role in the development of their HEHA trip planning app.
                li <strong><a href="https://riftrefunds.co.uk" target="_blank" rel="noopener">RIFT</a></strong> &#9758; Led their digital transformation, enabling hundreds of thousands to self service tax refund claims.
                li <strong><a href="https://laced.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Laced</a></strong> &#9758; Built their digital platform from the ground up and helped them scale to handle hundreds of millions in transactions.
                li <strong><a href="https://allocate.co.uk" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Allocate</a></strong> &#9758; Pulled out of a technical debt crisis and put a sustainable, modern foundation in place.

        .grid__item
          .card
            .card__aside
              .card__image-container
                img.card__image(src="/assets/images/logos/holidayextras.svg", alt="Holiday Extras logo" width="80" height="80" loading="lazy")
            .card__content
              h3 Holiday Extras <span class="card__dates">2013 - 2016</span>
              p I joined Holiday Extras as a Web Developer in 2013, working primarily on their airport hotel and parking booking system.
              p During my employment I was promoted to Software Engineer, and then Software Architect, where I helped to technical decision making across the organisation.

              p <a href="https://bitbrawn.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Visit Holiday Extras</a>.

