            .card__content
              h3 Parable <span class="card__dates">2022 - 2023</span>
              p An analytics platform for blog posts. Tracks actual readership and provides insights for writers. Built over a year, launched in 2022, <a href="/posts/my-first-failed-product">shut down in 2023</a> due to lack of product-market fit.

        .grid__item
