            .card__aside
              .card__image-container
                img.card__image(src="/assets/images/logos/howdy.svg", alt="Howdy logo" width="38" height="29" loading="lazy")
            .card__content
              h3 Howdy <span class="card__dates">2017 - 2022</span>
              p A simple tool that brings web contact forms to life with validation and email delivery. Developed at Leaf for small businesses; organically grew to 100+ users before winding down.

        .grid__item
